### Place an Order - Single Book
POST http://localhost:5052/api/orders/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Place an Order - Multiple Books (Shopping Cart)
POST http://localhost:5052/api/orders/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": 15,
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

